data.description: Welcome Ponder, Texas. This hidden gem features a spacious 1.06-acre lot on Stoney Acres Rd, providing an ideal canvas for your country living dreams. Revel in abundant space and privacy, perfect for lush gardens, family gatherings, and pets to roam freely. With a little TLC and creativity, this cozy home can be transformed into your dream residence or a lucrative investment opportunity. Tucked away from the city's hustle and bustle, this property offers a serene retreat while remaining conveniently close to nearby amenities and the charm of Ponder. Picture the endless potential this property holds, whether you seek a peaceful getaway, an investment with small-town charm.Embrace the warm, welcoming community of Ponder, celebrated for its excellent schools and relaxed pace of life. Yet, you're still within easy reach of the Dallas-Fort Worth Metroplex for work and entertainment. Consider the long-term value of owning over an acre of land in this rapidly growing area.
